  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/e9cafdb7d0f70d46bc84d80b004cecf5.poster.avif?t=1762538853\" width=610 height=171 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/e9cafdb7d0f70d46bc84d80b004cecf5.webm?t=1762538853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Embrace the role of dreadful cult leader!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Today you are in charge of Seaweed Bloaters... Or Knights of Hedone…Doesn’t matter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now your prodigal minion needs to stay on top! Beware, you are not the only one in this challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/4a75b59f7f7d4009690eb00c892f4eab.poster.avif?t=1762538853\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/4a75b59f7f7d4009690eb00c892f4eab.webm?t=1762538853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/4a75b59f7f7d4009690eb00c892f4eab.mp4?t=1762538853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Delve down the tower of doom.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use cards to help your loyal worshiper survive the turmoil. Send other players' minions to their doom at the bottom of the pit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/ae7c81060979704749abb7536107a49b.poster.avif?t=1762538853\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/ae7c81060979704749abb7536107a49b.webm?t=1762538853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/ae7c81060979704749abb7536107a49b.mp4?t=1762538853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Say your prayers!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just be respectful! And keep your cult a secret to everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/26de176e400f744d2f54005beb220f81.poster.avif?t=1762538853\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/26de176e400f744d2f54005beb220f81.webm?t=1762538853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918960/extras/26de176e400f744d2f54005beb220f81.mp4?t=1762538853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>And finally…FEED THE GODS!</strong></h2>",
